# Industrial Knowledge Intelligence

## Prototype Documentation

---

# Project Overview

Industrial Knowledge Intelligence is an AI-powered document intelligence platform that enables engineers, maintenance teams, and safety officers to instantly search and understand industrial documentation using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

The prototype converts industrial documents into a searchable knowledge base and answers user questions with source citations.

---

# Objectives

* Centralize industrial knowledge.
* Reduce document search time.
* Improve maintenance efficiency.
* Assist safety and compliance teams.
* Provide AI-powered document search.

---

# Key Features

### Document Upload

Users can upload industrial PDF documents.

### Document Processing

The system extracts text from uploaded documents.

### Semantic Search

Relevant document sections are retrieved using vector similarity search.

### AI Question Answering

Users can ask natural language questions.

### Source Citations

Every AI response includes the relevant document source.

---

