## Frontend

* Next.js
* React
* Tailwind CSS

## Backend

* FastAPI
* Python

## AI

* LangChain
* Sentence Transformers
* OpenAI / Ollama

## Database

* ChromaDB

## Document Processing

* PyMuPDF

