# Project Workflow

### Step 1

Upload Industrial PDF

↓

### Step 2

Extract Text

↓

### Step 3

Split into Chunks

↓

### Step 4

Generate Embeddings

↓

### Step 5

Store in ChromaDB

↓

### Step 6

User asks a Question

↓

### Step 7

Retrieve Relevant Chunks

↓

### Step 8

Generate AI Answer

↓

### Step 9

Display Response with Citations

