# API Endpoints

## Upload Document

POST

```
/upload
```

Response

```json
{
    "status":"uploaded"
}
```

---

## Ask Question

GET

```
/ask?question=...
```

Response

```json
{
    "answer":"...",
    "sources":[]
}
```

